name: Bunny League BETA
description:
Controls: Use left and right arrow to move. Left click to select options.

Story:  A group of astronauts called Bunny League make a trip to their moon to recolect the famous and extra delisious golden carrots, that only grow once a year. These bunnies are already used to this tradition since decades, but this time the trip went wrong. The space ship broke and these bunny have to "float" their way into their home planet and face all kinds of enemies. No bunny is excluded from inmersing themselves into the vast and dark space, but if they make it safe to their home they will be able to enjoy a dotation of super carrots with the rest of the community.
